Name: Strike Arrow II
Desc:
Shoots arrows several times in a row after using Strike Arrow to effectively suppress enemies. Temporarily enables you to reuse the skill after using Strike Arrow and also activates Arrow Fragment.
Required Skills: Strike Arrow Lv. 20 or above
Lv. 20 Effect: Can learn the 3rd Job skill, Strike Arrow III
